  <brief_title>Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of DWP05195 in Subjects With Post-Herpetic Neuralgia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Clinical Trial for Evaluation of Efficacy and Safety of DWP05195 in Postherpetic Neuralgia: Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Randomized, Multi-center, Exploratory Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
